title: Statement by the Press Secretary on the Visit of President Goodluck Jonathan of Nigeria to the White House | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
June 04, 2011

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on the Visit of President Goodluck Jonathan of Nigeria to the White House




President Obama will welcome President Goodluck Jonathan of Nigeria to the White House on Wednesday, June 8.Â  The President looks forward to consulting with President Jonathan on the latest regional and global developments, and deepening our strong bilateral partnership.
